title: 2021 Week 9 Preview
itunes:title: 2021 Week 9 Preview
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview every single upcoming game of week 9 starting with the primetime games. The draft kicks off in style as Marc tilts the show on its head and surprise picks the Browns. We have our first official lock off!
